Simple math problem. 

Use the recurrence, we have:
a2 = 2a1-a0+2c1
a3 = 3a1-2a0+4c1+2c2
...
an = na1-(n-1)a0+2(n-1)c1+2(n-2)c2+...+2c_{n-1}

On the other hand, since
2a1+2c1 = a0+a2
2a2+2c2 = a1+a3
...
2an+2cn = a_{n-1}+a_{n+1},
we have:
a1+an = a0+a_{n-1}-2(c1+...+cn)

From these two equations, we have:
a1 = na0+a_{n+1}-2(c1+...+cn)-2[(n-1)c1+(n-2)c2+...+c_{n-1}]


